FT  29 FEB 92 / World Stock Markets: South Africa
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
JOHANNESBURG remained generally steady, with gold stocks showing strong
gains following the rise in the bullion price. The all-gold index added 10
to 1,239. The overall index rose 15 to 3,597, while industrials put on 17 to
4,418.
</TEXT>
