reasonably priced video telephones for the consumer market. The group did
not, however, rule out the possibility that it may market Betacom's
telephones 'in some regions'.
Betacom, which has marketing strength in Germany, could in turn sell
Amstrad's fax machines'We look upon Amstrad as being a stronger holder of
our shares (than Cannon Street Investments),' said Mr Roger Roland, Betacom
chairman.
