against net profits of Dollars 149m for the same period a year earlier. The
restructuring charge totalled Dollars 250m at the net level. Woolworth had
warned of the charge, but the shares still eased Dollars 7/8 to Dollars 28
1/2 at close of trade.
Woolworth's sales for the final quarter rose from Dollars 3.06bn to Dollars
3.14bn, while sales for the year were Dollars 9.92bn against Dollars 9.79bn.
