interested in part of the group which also includes an interest in
exhibitions.
Emap has made a bid for all of MBC in partnership with Mr Brian Gilbert, a
former chairman of MBC. It is expected that after the deal is complete the
partners will divide up the parts in which they are most interested. Emap
would almost certainly be interested in the exhibitions and in titles such
as Architect's Journal and Media Week.
